<div id="ftn53">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/Ecoute%20de%20Marie%20partie%201.docx#_ftnref53" name="_ftn53"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[53]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="IT"> Cf. S.<span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Meo</span>, “<i>Madre di Dio</i>” dans <i>Nuovo dizionario di mariologia</i>, a cura di de Fiores, ed. san Paolo 1985, p.731-739</span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn54">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a title="" href="file:///D:/Users/FRANCOISE/Documents/EDITIONS/livres/A%20l'%C3%A9coute%20de%20Marie/Ecoute%20de%20Marie%20partie%201.docx#_ftnref54" name="_ftn54"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: FR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">[54]</span></span><!--[endif]--></a><span lang="IT"> H.<span style="text-transform: uppercase;">Denzinger - A.Schönmetzger</span>, <i>Enchiridion Symbolorum, Definitionum et declarationum de rebus fidei et morum, Herder</i>, (= DS) § 150. </span></p>
</div>
<div id="ftn55">
